quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,267,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e tottiree ko laaЙ“i ummaade ko paggiti Й—on e ko Min njaltinani on ka leydi, wotee paande ko soЙ“i ko ngam nafkude heen on ngonah nanngooЙ“e Й—um si wonah on meerni heen, ngannde Alla ko yondaniiЙ—o MantaaЙ—o"
  2,268,"Seytaane na fodana on baasal o yamira on pankare, Alla noon na fodana on yaafuya ummaade e Makko e Й“ural Alla ko jaacЙ—o ko O Ganndo"
  2,269,"Hombo totta ГұeeГұal mbo O wela kala tottaaЙ—o ГұeeГұal o tottaa ma moЖҙЖҙere mawnde, siftortah Й—um si wonah joman hakkiillaaji"
  2,270,"Kala ko tottirЙ—on e nafake wolla takkuЙ—on e takkere pellet Alla na anndi Й—uum, woodanaani tooГұooЙ“e wallooЙ“e"
  2,271,Si on Й“annginii sadakeeji na ЖҙЖҙi si on cuuЙ—i Й—i tottuЙ—on Й—i waasЙ“e ko Й—uum Й“uri on moЖҙЖҙande O hafrana on bonЙ—i mon Alla na humpitii ko golloton ko
  2,272,"A fawaaki peewal mum en kono ko Alla feewnata mbo O faala, kala ko tottirЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere ko ko*e mon woodani on nafkatah si wonah ngam Alla kala ko tottirЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere tottite Й—um e mbaadi timmundi onon de on tooГұetaake"
  2,273,"Woodanii waasЙ“e suraaЙ“e gaa e laawol Alla Й“e mbaawah yaade e leydi hee, majjuЙ“e na cikka koЙ“e alЙ—uЙ“e sabu Й—uurnaade aduna ana anndiraЙ“e maandeeji mum en Й“e Гұaagataaka yimЙ“e e mbaadi cattundi kala ko tottirЙ—on Alla na anndi Й—um"